Version 1.9.7                                                       2005-07-18
==============================================================================

1.    NEW FEATURES
      none
                               
2.    CHANGES
     
2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES
      
      CR0003360 
      openMDX/Ant's JRE
      
      The openMDX/Ant build expects JRE 1.2 being installed.
      
      Now openMDX/Ant
      1. uses JRE 1.2 if installed 
      2. uses Ant's JRE otherweise to cross compile for JRE 1.2 
      and
      * creates JRE 1.2 deliverables 
      
