Version 1.5.2                                                       2004-11-04
==============================================================================

1.    NEW FEATURES
      none
      
2.    CHANGES  
     
2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES
      
      CR0002546
      Deliverable and distribution directories  
      
      The reference "distribution.from-openmdx" (based on ${openmdx.home} in 
      the "-distribution-" target should be replaced by 
      "distribution.from-home" (based on ${project.home}.  
      
      A pre-requisite is, that ${deliver.dir} and ${src.archive.dir} are 
      ${project.home} based, as oppesed to ${openmdx.home} based. 

      CR0002714 
      ant library location  
      
      Put the ant libraries at their new locations according to the platform 
      specific thirdparty library pattern:
      * apache/jre-1.2/ant/lib/ant.jar 
      * ant/jre-1.2/contribution/lib/ant-contrib.jar 

2.1.  FIXED BUGS
      none
      
2.2.  DEPRECATED FEATURES
      none      

2.3   REMOVED FEATURES
      none

